research_insight_text_link.research_insight_description: AgriSync is focused on developing an integrated customer support system tailored for field-centric business sectors. Their R&D efforts are concentrated on a computer network that connects customers requiring product or service support with advisors. These advisors are equipped with devices designed to interface seamlessly with the server computer, enhancing the support experience. This technology aims to streamline the support process for businesses and equipment dealers, aligning with AgriSync's platform for ticketing and remote assistance.
